          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "坐镇荆襄，成霸业，威服列邦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "战国纷纷意不合，争夺疆土动干戈。威服邻邦成霸业，太平安固锦山河。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤，楚王熊旅。恼恨斗越椒，兴兵犯上，欲夺孤王社稷。幸喜皇天保佑，灭却"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "老贼，奏凯回朝。众家功臣，须得分功论赏。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内侍，宣众功臣上殿！"
        },
        {
          "character": "内侍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王有旨，众功臣上殿！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众将 （内同白） 来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众将同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "众将",
          "line_type": "同念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "扫灭狼烟干戈靖，卷旗息鼓享太平。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众卿少礼。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "将臣等宣上殿来，有何军情议论？"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且喜干戈宁靖，奏凯还朝。孤今日大排筵宴，庆贺功臣，与众卿痛饮。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "多谢大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内侍，看宴侍候。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（〖水龙吟〗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内侍，宣徐娘娘上渐台。"
        },
        {
          "character": "内侍",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王有旨：宣徐娘娘上渐台。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐妃上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐妃",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "忽听大王宣，迈步上银安。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐妃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梓童少礼，速登渐台。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内侍，看酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "吓，众卿，今日与众卿饮宴，快乐非常。欲命徐妃，与诸卿进酒一杯，以取君"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣同乐。"
        },
        {
          "character": "众将",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣等有何德能，敢劳娘娘进酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤心已定。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梓童进酒。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "君臣对坐饮琼浆，"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "分功论赏古之常。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孤今日宴群臣喜洋洋。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（唐狡调戏徐妃，徐妃去唐狡盔缨，上台付耳。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵！"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮原板",
          "musical_style": "西皮原板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "叫梓童回宫去孤有主张。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐妃下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢掌灯。今日之宴，非比寻常。众卿各将盔缨摘下，就名为摘缨大会。若无"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "盔缨者，罚酒三觥。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（内侍取各盔缨，呈。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掌灯！"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "笑",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵哈哈哈哈！"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "内侍将宴撤下，众卿各退朝房。退班。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（楚庄王下。众将同下。唐狡比式。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
