    {
      "scene_index": 2,
      "label": "第二场",
      "characters_present": [
        "徐妃",
        "楚庄王"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（二宫女、徐妃同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐妃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "适才殿上进酒浆，"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐妃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "胆大狂徒起不良。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐妃",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "等候大王问端详。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（内侍、楚庄王同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "宴罢了文武臣神清气爽，"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "问梓童因何故面带彷徨？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐妃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "启大王：适才殿上，那胆大狂徒调戏妾身。不知大王怎样发落？"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "孤念他酒醉，一概不究。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐妃",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "他调戏国母，就该将他问斩。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "梓童，吓。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮正板",
          "musical_style": "西皮正板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "劝梓童休得要把本奏上，"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮正板",
          "musical_style": "西皮正板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "听孤王把前情细说端详："
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮正板",
          "musical_style": "西皮正板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "只杀得众将官死故逃亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮正板",
          "musical_style": "西皮正板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "天降下养由基英雄小——"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "将，"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "清河桥比箭法老贼身亡。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "就有那无名辈酒后癫狂。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "怕的是杀功臣遗笑邻邦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮二六板",
          "musical_style": "西皮二六板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "劝梓童把此事付与汪洋。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮摇板",
          "musical_style": "西皮摇板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孤与你同偕老日久天长。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [
        {
          "edge": "徐妃→楚庄王",
          "turns": 3
        },
        {
          "edge": "楚庄王→徐妃",
          "turns": 2
        }
      ],
