    {
      "scene_index": 5,
      "label": "第五场",
      "characters_present": [
        "唐狡"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（唐狡上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐狡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺，唐狡。今有我主与晋兵交战，待我登高一望。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（楚庄王上，先蔑打，楚庄王下，先蔑下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐狡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且住。前面败的我主，后面乃是先蔑追赶。此时若不搭救，等待何时？"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐狡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "唉！先蔑休走，你老爷来也！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（唐狡耍刀，下。）"
        }
      ],
      "interactions": [],
      "stats": {
