    {
      "scene_index": 7,
      "label": "第七场",
      "characters_present": [
        "唐狡",
        "报子",
        "楚庄王",
        "连尹襄老"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四龙套、连尹襄老、楚庄王同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小将立功劳，孤王喜心梢。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "先蔑擒到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "押上来。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刀斧手押先蔑同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "战鼓不住咚咚打，"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "先蔑老儿听根芽："
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "此时为何被孤拿？"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "立斩人头正军法。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刀斧手推先蔑同下，斩。报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小将军到。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有请。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（唐狡上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "一见小将喜心下，"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "孤王言来听根芽："
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "西皮快板",
          "musical_style": "西皮快板",
          "style_family": "西皮",
          "text": "你就是孤王救苦救难观世音、活菩萨。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "小将军，孤与你素不相识，你为何舍命救我？"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "适才蒙你来救驾"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐狡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大王可记得，摘缨会之故事乎？"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊，哈哈，呀！想当年摘缨会之时，孤若查明将他问斩，孤家焉有今日？"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呵，小将军，孤今封你统兵大元帅，参理朝政。"
        },
        {
          "character": "唐狡",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "谢大王。"
        },
        {
          "character": "连尹襄老",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "慢着。今日他为元帅，正管我一头。不免与大王说明，替我讲个情儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "连尹襄老",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "臣启大王：想臣那日出兵之际，小将曾来讨令，老臣因他年幼，将他叉出帐去。"
        },
        {
          "character": "连尹襄老",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "今日他为元帅，老臣正他所管，臣恐公报私仇，求大王做主。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这有何难。小将军，今将襄老拨在你帐下听用。倘有差错，按军法从事。"
        },
        {
          "character": "连尹襄老",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好，好！倒闹了个倒讬。"
        },
        {
          "character": "楚庄王",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "后帐摆宴，与小将军贺功。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
